Class ProteinChangeAllele

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.charite.compbio.jannovar.hgvs.protein.variant.ProteinChangeAllele
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConvertibleToHGVSString, Iterable<ProteinChange>, Collection<ProteinChange>, List<ProteinChange>

    public final class ProteinChangeAllele
extends Object
implements ConvertibleToHGVSString, List<ProteinChange>
    Contains the ProteinChanges on one allee. Examples:
    • [(Gly28Val);(Asn26His)]
    • [Gly28Val;Asn26His]
    • [Gly28Val;(Asn26His)]

    Manuel Holtgrewe
